Browse all available datasets of ONS census 2021 data

Source: R/coe_census_datasets.R
coe_census_datasets.Rd

Browse all available datasets of ONS census 2021 data

Usage

coe_census_datasets(description = TRUE)

Arguments

description

Logical. If TRUE, (the default), a tibble is returned that contains ONS ids and corresponding dataset descriptions. If false, a character vector containing only ONS ids is returned.

Value

A tibble of ONS ids and dataset descriptions, or a character vector of ONS ids.

Examples

coe_census_datasets() |>
  dplyr::glimpse()

#> Columns: 2
